Description: The die-hard romantic in her is lulled into sense of euphoria with the luxurious La Lune. The soft silks brush against her skin making her sigh at the emotions churning inside her. Designer duo Dolce&Gabbana offers 18 La Lune to the woman who waits with expectations on a warm, summer evening. The Eau de Toilette lures her into visions of wide, flowery fields of freedom and fulfillment. The citrusy sweetness of bergamot blends with the crispness of apple to give the fragrance a crunchy top note. The personality of this delicate scent is reflected in the heart notes of tropical tuberose, velvety rose and the pristine lily. The dry down finally brings to your senses a deep waft of musk, sandalwood and orris root. An element of leather, which comes as a mild surprise, anchors down the base note and lends character to the fragrance.  La Lune incites the romantic in you, the impeccably, elegant flacon seems to hold a glint that tugs the strings of your heart. Dolce&Gabbana take inspiration from the classic, apothecary bottle and add their own signature with the glossy jet pump and modern cap making the container simple yet supremely sophisticated.

Title: Hugo Deep Red EDP  -  50 ml(For Women)
Description: Audacious and razor-sharp, this luxury scent embodies the essence of the self-confident woman who has the world wrapped around her fingers. Hugo Deep Red is a symbol of the enigma and sheer power that she effortlessly radiates because it is her very nature. Created by Alain Astori and Beatrice Piquet, this sophisticated Eau de Parfum is specially concocted for the celebrated house of Hugo Boss. A top note that blends tart notes of blackcurrant, zesty mandarin orange, fruity hints of pear, distinct notes of clementine and a trace of blood orange. Flowing into the heart note, experience the delight of floral tuberose, soft and sweet hints of freesia that are balanced with hints of hibiscus seed and spicy ginger. Finally, the base note mixes the rich aroma of sandalwood with warming cedar extracts, soothing but heavy notes of musk and creamy vanilla. This exquisite fruity floral fragrance is ideal for a romantic and sensual night out in the town. The alluring fragrance is ensconced in an cylindrical vial that is painted a deep hue of crimson radiating intensity and seduction. A simple silver stopper along with minimal silver lettering decorate this bottle. Unpretentious and provocative, Hugo Deep Red is for the woman who knows exactly what she wants.

Title: Olay Total Effects 7 in 1 Anti-ageing Serum(50 ml)
Description: The Olay Story A brainchild of a chemist, Olay was born out of love and was Graham Wulff’s gift to his doting wife. Graham wanted to create a new beauty product that would leave his wife’s skin nourished and moisturized without leaving a greasy feel. Graham and Dinah started an extensive research and finally created the legendary Oil of Olay Beauty Fluid. Olay is today a recognized and trusted brand and promises the dainty ladies skin that glows with good health. Olay provides its consumers products that are safe and ensures that each product manufactured, undergoes a thorough quality test. Celebrate beauty and pamper your skin with Olay. Olay Total Effects 7 in 1 Anti-ageing Serum Olay Total Effects brings you a wide range of products that make your skin look its best always. 7 in 1 Anti-ageing Serum promises you younger looking skin. Look gorgeous as ever with a regular application of this skin care product. Claim Fighting signs of ageing, Olay Total Effects 7 in 1 Anti-ageing Serum endows you with youthful skin that is soft and supple. Features and Benefits - This serum fights signs of ageing to give you younger looking skin. - Olay Total Effects 7 in 1 Anti-ageing Serum gives you an even skin tone and reduces blemishes and spots. - Reducing dryness and preventing flaky skin, this serum provides your skin intense moisturization. - Imparting glow to your skin, Olay Total Effects 7 in 1 Anti-ageing Serum gives your dull skin life. - See visible results and look young as this serum reduces fine lines and smoothens wrinkles. Regime Follow this simple regime for glowing skin. Just wash your face with Olay Total Effects Cleanser and apply Total Effects Serum to give your skin that special boost. You can use Total Effects Eye Cream to reduce dark circles, fine lines and wrinkles around your eyes. Finally, you need to apply Olay Total Effects Skin Cream to prevent excess dryness and keep your skin moisturized. Directions Apply Olay Total Effects 7 in 1 Anti-ageing Serum on a clean face and neck for supple and glowing looking skin. Tips and Advice It is essential to wash your face with a good cleanser before you apply Olay Total Effects 7 in 1 Anti-ageing Serum to enjoy good results. Warnings Avoid contact with eyes and if Olay Total Effects 7 in 1 Anti-ageing Serum comes in contact, make sure that you rinse your eyes thoroughly with water. Incase of any occurrence of skin and eye irritations, please discontinue using this product. Make sure that you keep this serum out of reach of young children. Ingredients Enriched with vitamin B3, pro-vitamin B5 and vitamin E, this serum also has the goodness of sucrose polycottonseedate, c13-14 isoparaffin, panthenol, tocopheryl acetate, stearyl alcohol, titanium dioxide, dimethiconol, benzyl alcohol and other chemicals that nourish your skin and make it look fabulous.

Description: Fragrances are created from essential oils present in plants, flowers, fruits, barks, roots, and animal secretions. And what precious pricey substances they are! In Grasse, France, the centre of the World Perfumery Industry, workers rise early to pick Jasmine before dawn. When the sun peeks over the horizon, the flower loses twenty percent of its aroma. A skilled harvester can pick about a pound of flowers in forty five minutes, or five thousand tiny blossoms. But only a few drops of essence will emerge after processing. Eight hundred pounds of Jasmine flowers, or four million flowers, yield just one pound of concentrated oil. And the price of the essences. One pound of this oil, called Jasmine Absolute will fetch from 80,000 to 1, 00,000, depending on quality, while Rose Absolute can cost as much as 2,50,000 to 3,00,000 per pound.
